Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:07.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\Nwithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:19.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:23.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:31.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:37.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:40.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:44.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:55.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:01:02.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:08.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\Nwhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:11.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:19.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:25.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible \NSpiritual Pressure he has...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:40.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really a Menos Grande?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:42.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:50.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,His upper body disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:53.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He split?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:57.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Were there two of them\Nfrom the beginning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a way to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:05.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Renze Forumeru Venti Gral!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:06.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Haizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Instant Regeneration!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:28.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:29.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:31.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:32.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:39.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuken...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:42.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Addressing your father by his name\Nwithout any sign of respect?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:45.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as always,\Naren't you, Uryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:58.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to worry about\Nhis Instant Regeneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to deal with him\Nbefore he uses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:07.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:15.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWhy do you have Quincy powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:20.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hate Quincies so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because their skills aren't profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:29.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You hated Quincies so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:35.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you had discarded\Nyour Quincy powers long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said that you were stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:47.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"I had no interest" and\Nthat "you had no talent."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:57.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, my powers won't\Ndisappear as easily as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuken Ishida...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:06.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I like it or not,\Nthat is the name of the man
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:09.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who is the successor to all the powers\Nand skills of his predecessor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:10.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soken Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:18.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And the only person who is allowed\Nto call himself "The Last Quincy."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:25.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:31.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a Quincy like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:36.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Is that what you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:45.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But becoming a full-fledged Quincy\Nis no easy matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Quincy Cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:06.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed that Hollow in a single strike...\NI could only scratch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:11.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are inexperienced...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:19.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to Soul Society inexperienced\Nand lost your inexperienced power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:32.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were moved by your small pride\Nand ended up accomplishing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:43.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can restore your lost power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:46.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:50.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:06:00.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:03.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:09.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Swear to me that you will not involve\Nyourself with Soul Reapers from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:36.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not fight in the middle of town!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:36.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:41.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you run away,\NIchigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:46.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to your Soul Reaper form!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:51.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!\NWhy does this always happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:56.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:00.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:05.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:10.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kon's Spiritual Pressure is\Nright next to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:14.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kon? What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:21.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:26.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that you've tricked me\Nby saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:46.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... I've been eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:49.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop sleep talking while you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:59.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kon! What are you doing\Nin Ichigo's body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:03.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?! A gigantic Hollow\Nis chasing me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:09.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic! You're a mod-soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:14.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! He's not your usual Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's kind of fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:22.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at running away,\Nbut he can keep up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:32.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were lying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:36.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help you if you're having problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:37.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As they say, "Even chance meetings\Nare the result of karma,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:45.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and "One who is kind to others is\Nsure to be rewarded."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why would I want to be helped\Nby the likes of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:55.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Ichigo Kurosaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:00.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:05.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Running away isn't any different than\Nwhat I've been doing all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a turn there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:58.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally became a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:04.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to take your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:15.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Will he be all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:18.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us!\NWe can handle one or two Hollows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Noba, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:20.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a silly trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:26.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that you can\Nget away from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:34.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't any help at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't believe me when\NI told him that I wasn't Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:51.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is his mask partially off?!\NI can see his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:12:01.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been chasing you around, waiting for\Nyou to turn into your Soul Reaper form...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:14.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't return to\Nyour Soul Reaper form, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:24.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to turn your bones to dust\Nwhile you're still human!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:28.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! My legs won't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PROTECTION
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:58.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to wear it at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That person...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:03.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Hollow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but Ichigo is out right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:16.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not much of a substitute,\Nbut do you mind playing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:31.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't introduced myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:35.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Isshin...Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:55.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with\Nthis Spiritual Pressure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:59.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's another huge one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:00.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a Hollow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:06.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...\NDid he only notice just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:11.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this guy really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:16.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Spiritual Pressure of\Nthe Soul Reaper who just appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:19.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:21.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:25.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!\NWhere are you going, Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was still talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:28.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I'm not finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:33.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:38.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever organization it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't plan on joining your "Visored"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:51.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:55.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:20.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hirako.\NIs this Ms. Sarugaki's cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:23.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:32.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped...\NSay what you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:47.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:52.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Ichigo Kurosaki's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:54.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,PROTECTION
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Take this, Kon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:03.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This charm was something
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant for you \Nto have to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:08.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He even knows my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:13.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-When did you notice\Nthat I wasn't Ichigo--?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:18.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:23.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the first time\NI saw you in Ichigo's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:26.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,on the day we went to visit\NMasaki's grave... Since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Think back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:36.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you were in Ichigo's body,\NI've never called you Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite my looks, I'm pretty sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:44.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that so, friendly trio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:49.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he knew about us, too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:55.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a pretty \Nawkward meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:06.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... If his father is\Na Soul Reaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that Ichigo Kurosaki\Nis a Shinketsu, a true blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:17.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I can understand\Nwhy I lost to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:20.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the Hollows that I've met,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:28.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you're the oldest, dirtiest, \Nand the most annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:35.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However...\NIsshin, I am not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:40.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here tonight \Nto kill Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:44.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As his father,\NI'm sure you know where he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:46.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:51.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where he is...\NHe's not a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:56.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we have a hands-off policy\Nin our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:18:00.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You cling to your daughters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:03.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu and Karin are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:04.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather a special case!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As different as night and day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:08.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you aren't \Ninterested in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:15.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a problem\Nif you didn't fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:29.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:35.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty big talk for a Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:43.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think\NI'm any normal Hollow, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:04.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! This is the true form\Nof my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What incredible size...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:12.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's as large as \Nthose Menos I saw before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:13.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or larger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:16.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Menos?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:20.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:23.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,An Arrancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:30.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a group of Hollows aiming\Nto attain Soul Reaper powers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:31.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by removing their masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:39.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? \NYou're pretty knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:49.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you probably know that\Nyou can't win against my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:52.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A zanpakuto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:55.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredibly huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:57.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:03.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A zanpakuto's size equals\Nthe size of one's Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:12.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is quite obvious that puny zanpakuto\Ncannot beat my zanpakuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:16.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:20.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that even though\Nyou know the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:31.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you're a fool who doesn't have\Nany Soul Reaper common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:37.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let your death give you understanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:55.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you the basics...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:08.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-level Soul Reapers all control\Nthe size of their zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:15.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If they didn't, they'd all be \Nswinging swords as large as buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:21.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:26.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell how strong your opponent is\Nby the size of his zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:46.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Only then can you talk to me\Nabout Soul Reapers, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:07.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you at age 16
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:13.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and we had\Nan eternal love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:18.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath\Ncherry blossoms petals
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:24.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,gently fluttering downward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:29.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That steep and sunny hill
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:35.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where I ran up to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:40.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...And our shadows at\Nthe corner of the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:46.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they are still unchanged\Neven today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:52.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You, me,\Nand cherry blossom days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:57.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we dance\Nand sway in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.37,0:23:03.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding in our heart\Nthe unseen future,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:11.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we look up at the pink sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:23.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of difficult terms appeared today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:24.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall therefore explain to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:27.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,what the "Visored" and the "Arrancar"\Nare in the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:29.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would like to attend\Nthe Kisuke Urahara Talk Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:31.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Get an application when you buy \Nsomething at Urahara's Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:33.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and send it to the address below.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:35.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to send one in!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:37.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!\N- Golden...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:39.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been doing lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:41.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:43.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed my sunglasses,\Nbut no one noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.99,0:23:47.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunglasses? How dull...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:48.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:49.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:51.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My sideburns.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:54.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wearing them \Nin a different style now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:56.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't really that different...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.48,0:24:01.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's the Dull Lieutenant Trio!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.51,0:24:02.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dull?!